Text.string: Recruit! Help me find my special little guy?
My pet Kevin is missing!
Kevin Samantha Claptrap! You get back here this instant!
Vault Hunter. You need to use a cryo weapon to slow him down!
You got him! Oh, Kevin! My life was utterly devoid of meaning without you!
Vault Hunter. These “Kevin” creatures must be destroyed. They're reproducing at an alarming rate.
Kevin's a papa? I'm a grand-papa?! Oh, I've never been happier!
Yes. Well, as I was saying: the Kevins must be captured and dumped into space.
What?! No! No, no! I'll get you for this, Tannis!
I found a new best friend! I named him Kevin. And now I don't need any of YOU chumps to be my friend anymore! Haha! Ha! Hahaha!||—But also, he's gone missing!
These creatures are important to Claptrap for... some reason, but this is an infestation, and they must be disposed of.
Ah, there you are. Just drop those monsters into the biohazard disposal chute and dump them into space.
I guess now we know who the REAL monster is! It's YOU, Tannis!
No, you won't.
Probably not! But if anyone needs me, I'll be launching my OWN search party! I'm gonna save ALL the Kevins!
Papa's looking for little Kevin!
Where's my Kevin? Where's my tiny Kevin?!
No more hide and seek, Kevin.
I'm going to count to three, Kevin! One. Two. Three!||—There. I hope you're happy. You made me COUNT!
Kevin!
Keeeeevinnn!
Baby Kevin!
Come to papa, Kevin! Come to papa.
Here, Kevin, Kevin, Kevin!
Come here, Kevin! Come here so the mean lady can't kill you!
That's it! We're in a fight, Kevin! We're fighting now!
You get out here right now! I am so angry I could punch a Kevin!
Don't worry, though! He almost never eats faces anymore!
I believe you're near one of those Kevin creatures now.
One of those Kevins is near your location.
Keep an eye out for a Kevin in your vicinity.
My readings indicate that you are near a Kevin creature.
Keep an eye out—there's a Kevin nearby.
Do you hear something? I believe there's a Kevin near you.
Watch for a disgusting Kevin creature near there.
One of Claptrap's monsters should be nearby now.
No. No. They're nearly impervious to damage. You have to freeze them!
I don't want to tell you again, Vault Hunter. You have to freeze them.
You're not going to take them out that way.
Wrong again. You cannot use conventional firearms against these creatures.
Once again, you'll have to use a cryo weapon to freeze them solid.
Excellent work! Now grab it!
Frozen solid. Perfect. Pick it up!
You know the drill. Please collect that Kevin.
My readings indicate that you have now captured all Kevins onboard. To ensure their total destruction, they must be expelled into the merciless vacuum of space.
Good night, my sweet wriggly princes.
Claptrap, next time you feel like bringing an unknown organism on board? Don't. If it happens again, you're going into the airlock with them!
Hngh. Yes, ma'am.
The ship is safer and far less disgusting thanks to you, Vault Hunter. Well done.
I've got one of them right over there. Go 'n' grab it, VH.
Aggh!
Cryo weapon's in that storage locker. It's all yours.
You need a cryo gun. It's right over there.
Happy to help you get rid of that li'l monster. Grab my cryo gun!
Now that you've got a cryo weapon, freeze Kevin in place, then snatch him up!
He's basically immune to damage, use cryo instead!
No, no! You have to use the cryo gun!
I told you! Use the cryo weapon!
Cryo, Vault Hunter. Freeze him!
Whatever you say, Claptrap.
Good work, Vault Hunter.
These aren't even your Kevin, Claptrap. They're his offspring.
I don't care! All Kevins are beautiful and perfect, and I'm going to save them!
Then we'll have to dispose of them, too.
Damn! Foiled again!
Good catch!
Ah! That must be Kevin! Let's go!
Claptrap, if these Kevins continue reproducing, we'll be more Kevin than crew within a week!
Good! Kevins are better than humans anyway!
You're hopeless.
Only a couple more to go!
That's nearly all of them.
Damn you, Tannis! DAMN YOU!
Yee-uck! What a disgusting creature!
Someone get this monster OUT OF MY BAR!
Ah, what fascinating specimen has infested our ship?! Thrilling!
Gross.
What the hell is that greasy li'l sumbitch?!
Gahh! Some gross wriggly thing just ran by!
What the hell is that thing?! Shoot it!
What the hell is that thing?!
That's Kevin! My best friend!
It's a disgustin' monster is what it is! And fast, too!
